revision.text:
{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2015}}
The '''1st Cavalry Brigade''' was a [[formation (military)|formation]] of the [[Royal Hungarian Army]] that participated in the [[Axis powers|Axis]] [[invasion of Yugoslavia]] during [[World War II]].{{sfn|Niehorster|2013}}

