{{Infobox tennis event|2016|Brest Challenger| | date=17 – 23 October | edition=2nd | surface=[[Tennis court#Hard courts|Hard]] | location=[[Brest, France]] | champs={{flagicon|SVK}} [[Norbert Gombos]] | champd={{flagicon|NED}} [[Sander Arends]] / {{flagicon|POL}} [[Mateusz Kowalczyk]] }}
The '''2016 [[Brest Challenger]]''' was a professional [[tennis]] tournament played on [[Tennis court#Hard courts|hard courts]]. It was the second edition of the tournament which was part of the [[2016 ATP Challenger Tour]]. It took place in [[Brest, France]] between 17 and 23 October 2016.
