The '''Akwambo festival''' is celebrated by the chiefs and peoples of Agona Nyakrom and Agona Swedru in the [[Central Region, Ghana|Central region]] of [[Ghana]].<ref name=Bak>{{cite web|title=Festivals in Ghana|url=http://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/tourism/festivals.php|publisher=www.ghanaweb.com|accessdate=27 December 2011}}</ref> The festival is celebrated in the month of August every year.<ref name=Bak/>

