{{Infobox company |name = Andorran Financial Authority |native_name = Autoritat Financera Andorrana |founded = 1989 |industry = [[Financial services]] |logo = |logo_size = |num_employees = |key_people = |location = |location_city = |location_country = [[Andorra]] |website = {{URL|https://www.afa.ad/}} }} '''Andorran Financial Authority''', known as ''Andorran National Institute of Finance'' (''INAF'') between 1989 and 2018, is a public financial institution founded in 1989 and provides functions of [[financial regulation]] and control of the [[financial sector]] in [[Andorra]]. <ref>{{Cite web |url=https://globaledge.msu.edu/global-resources/resource/6120 |title=Andorran National Institute of Finance (INAF) |accessdate=14 March 2017 }}</ref>
Its regulatory task was used for describing the government measures to solve the [[Banca Privada d'Andorra]] financial crisis in 2015. <ref>{{Cite web |url= |title=National Institute of Finance of Andorra explained the procedure of the measures of the government of Andorra aimed at combating financial crimes of Banca Privada D'Andorra |date=23 February 2016 }}</ref>
