'''Karjalan veljeskunta''' (''Karelian Brotherhood'') was an organization founded in 1907 as a [[Russian Orthodox]] society, whose goal was to [[Russification|russify]] [[Karelia]]s orthodox population.

The chief of the organization was bishop [[Kyprianos]] (Kiprian). Karjalan veljeskunta was dissolved when [[Finland]] obtained its independence in 1917.

