[[File:Wilhelm Froelich.jpg|right|thumb|Willian Frülich depicted by [[Hans Asper]]]]

'''William Frülich of Soleure''' ([[floruit|fl.]] 1544; '''Wilhelm Frölich''' in German) was a [[Swiss people|Swiss]] military leader; he was the commander of the [[Swiss mercenaries]] in [[France|French]] service at the [[Battle of Ceresole]].

